               ┌───────┐
Task 1 ───────▶│Thread │
               └───────┘
               ┌───────┐
Task 2 ───────▶│Thread │   (Fixed thread pool)
               └───────┘
               ┌───────┐
Task 3 ───────▶│Thread │
               └───────┘


✔ Easy
❌ Blocking
❌ Lots of context switching
❌ Not ideal for IO-heavy async workloads